FBIS4-61611 "drsov089_s_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-089 Daily Report 6 May 1994 Georgia Defense Minister Regarded as Russian Serviceman Defense Minister Regarded as Russian Serviceman LD0605202894 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1400 GMT 6 May 94 LD0605202894 Tbilisi IBERIA Georgian BFN [Text] Tbilisi, 6th [dateline as received] -- According to an announcement by the Department of Information of the Russian Defense Ministry, despite the fact that Lieutenant General Varden Nadibaidze has been appointed Georgian defense minister, he is still regarded as an officer of Russian Armed Forces because he has not taken an oath of loyalty to Georgia.
